{"title":"湖","authors":["金波"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":8,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金波"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的风景最美："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林中有一池圆圆的湖水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它亮得像面镜子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它绿得像块翡翠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微风吹过湖面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波纹一圈追着一圈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像一张发光的大唱片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在林中草地上旋转。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你听，这里播送出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么好听的音乐："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蟋蟀弹琴，小鸟唱歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啄木鸟敲着木琴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青蛙打着小鼓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假日里，我们常坐在湖边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手里捧着新摘的野果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面吃着野果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面听着这欢乐的音乐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数不清有多少雨点儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跑进了山下的水库，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村外的苇塘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和碧绿的小湖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听姐姐说，那小雨点儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送给我们许多礼物，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她把这些东西撒在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树林里、牧场上和绿色的山谷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨后，我们光着双脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到野外去散步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挎上个小竹篮儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去寻找雨点儿的礼物。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看！竹笋钻出了地面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木耳贴着老树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松林里捡到了小松蕈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧场上拾到了大蘑菇……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捡了满满一篮跑回家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请老爷爷看看这雨点儿的礼物。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是他说这不是雨点儿送来的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家乡的土地本来就这样富足！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}